        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>LymeX Authorization Act</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Health and Human Services to carry out prize competitions to accelerate innovation in the prevention, diagnosis, and treatment of Lyme disease. Lyme disease is a bacterial infection carried by ticks that can spread to joints, the heart, and the nervous system.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
